"answer":"要使$f(x)$为偶函数，需要满足$f(x) = f(-x)$。将$f(x) = (x-1)^2 + ax + \sin(x + \frac{\pi}{2})$代入$f(-x)$，得到$f(-x) = ((-x)-1)^2 + a(-x) + \sin(-x + \frac{\pi}{2})$。由于$\sin(x + \frac{\pi}{2}) = \cos(x)$，且$\cos(x)$是偶函数，$\sin(-x + \frac{\pi}{2}) = \sin(x + \frac{\pi}{2})$。因此，我们有$(x-1)^2 + ax + \cos(x) = ((-x)-1)^2 - ax + \cos(x)$。化简得到$x^2 - 2x + 1 + ax + \cos(x) = x^2 + 2x + 1 - ax + \cos(x)$。通过比较系数，得到$-2 + a = 2 - a$，解得$a = 2$。"]
